data.value: The Automatid Update All Files button works like this. Any MP3 file named in the format of "Artist - Title" or "Title by Artist" will have their title, and artist tags correctly updated. For example all the files should like something like "Bruno Mars - The Lazy Song.mp3." Also if you have a JPG file that has the same name as your MP3 in the same directory, it will be the image for your MP3. Example "Bruno - Mars The Lazy Song.jpg" is in the same directory as the MP3. Using Automatic Update will save changes immiedietly.
